    "scope_description" : "New Coworker is an AI assistant for small businesses. It uses these meeting scopes to schedule, update, and cancel Zoom meetings on behalf of the connected business owner (e.g. booking customer appointments captured by phone, SMS, or email) and to create invite links it can send to customers. The user scope is used to identify the connected account. Meeting data is used only to fulfill the owner’s scheduling requests; any stored data is kept in an RLS-protected, encrypted database and is deleted on request."
